name: TAO, BAGAY, HAYOP #2
description:
People's fascination with TV as entertainment and passing time freely as they binge watch, they go wander into la-la land.

We as humans are faced with daily challenges in life. Fortunately we were all designed to weather any kind of storm, to survive and thrive. We all have our own unique ways of coping with challenges.

TAO,BAGAY,HAYOP (Man, Thing, Animal) is a term or phrase embedded in Filipino culture whether in education or games.

Artistically shows how we cope as we solve each problems we face through entertainment that enhances our resilience.
